{"tid":517404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞雙賊元朗出沒　棍毆夜歸女劫走500人仔","createTime":"2018-01-02T09:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T09:36:52.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b487ccf0ea46fd68a0a8ec7c6db21f51b78d21dc","tid":517404,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T09:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180102/photo/bkn-20180102030221606-0102_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180102115452\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180102%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180102030221606-0102_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180102115452&h=0ffdf380&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">現場攸田東路。(陳家富攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n南亞兵團又犯案，元朗截劫夜歸女。昨(1日)深夜11時許，一名姓胡（37歲）女子，返家途經攸田東路近朗河路交界時，遭2名南亞裔男子攔途截劫，其中一人以木棍襲擊胡，再搶去其載有500元人民幣的手袋，2賊得手後逃去，女事主傷勢並無大礙，自行報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警員聞訊到場兜截無發現，胡無需送院在場助查；案件列行劫，由元朗警區刑事調查隊接手。警方根據事主提供資料，追查2名南亞賊下落，2人俱年約30歲，其中一人身高約1.7米及瘦身材，案發時身穿深色外套、戴黑色口罩及手持木棍，另一人則高約1.6米及瘦身材，案發時身穿深色外套。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180102/photo/bkn-20180102030221606-0102_00822_001_03p.jpg?20180102115452\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180102%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180102030221606-0102_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20180102115452&h=d6c63f8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180102/bkn-20180102030221606-0102_00822_001.html?refer=fn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180102%2Fbkn-20180102030221606-0102_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dfn2&d=nZRNgdHY6xtRP5JeSkPu010Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=226b1af4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180102/bkn-20180102030221606-0102_00822_001.html?refer=fn2</a>"},{"pid":"ad5c57c4629efa54986876b26987950512572fed","tid":517404,"uid":58071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T09:31:55.000Z","m